# Swift / Xcode
# (no `Packages/` rule — APFS is case-insensitive so it would also catch the
# lowercase `packages/` npm tree. SwiftPM downloads into `.build/`, so the
# legacy `Packages/` rule is unneeded.)
.build/
DerivedData/
*.xcodeproj/
*.xcworkspace/
sdks/swift/.actantffi/

